{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0019", "text": "爲愛事事已退讓 偏因那原則開仗", "structure": {"line_index": 19, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 2, 5, 4, 2, 3, 3, 5, 0, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["oi3", "si6", "si6", "ji5", "teoi3", "joeng6", "pin1", "jan1", "naa5", "jyun4", "zak1", "hoi1", "zoeng3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "事事", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "退讓", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "偏因", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "原則", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "開仗", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0018", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0020", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0020", "text": "今天這抉擇輪到我 比虛構戲劇還哀傷", "structure": {"line_index": 20, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 5, 4, 2, 0, 4, 5, 9, 3, 4, 4, 2, 0, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gam1", "tin1", "ze5", "kyut3", "zaak6", "leon4", "dou3", "ngo5", "bei2", "heoi1", "kau3", "hei3", "kek6", "waan4", "oi1", "soeng1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "今天", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "抉擇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輪到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "虛構", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "戲劇", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "哀傷", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0019", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0021", "paragraph_id": "para_05"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0021", "text": "原來是世間太荒謬", "structure": {"line_index": 21, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 0, 2, 4, 4, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["jyun4", "loi4", "si6", "sai3", "taai3", "fong1", "mau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "原來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "世間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "荒謬", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0020", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0022", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0022", "text": "你我分的手先最合理與溫柔", "structure": {"line_index": 22, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 3, 3, 9, 3, 4, 2, 5, 5, 3, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "ngo5", "fan1", "dik1", "sau2", "sin1", "zeoi3", "hap6", "lei5", "jyu5", "wan1", "jau4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "手先", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "合理", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "與", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "溫柔", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0021", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0023", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0023", "text": "每個爭鬥 誰來假裝妥協心不對口", "structure": {"line_index": 23, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 3, 4, 0, 0, 9, 3, 9, 4, 3, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mui5", "go3", "zang1", "dau3", "seoi4", "loi4", "gaa2", "zong1", "to2", "hip3", "sam1", "bat1", "deoi3", "hau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "每個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爭鬥", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "假裝", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "妥協", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "心", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對口", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0022", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0024", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0024", "text": "暗地也有傷口 無法善後", "structure": {"line_index": 24, "char_count": 10}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 5, 5, 3, 9, 0, 4, 2, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["am3", "dei6", "jaa5", "jau5", "soeng1", "hau2", "mou4", "faat3", "sin6", "hau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "暗地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傷口", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "無法", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "善後", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0023", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0025", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0025", "text": "跟你試過遷就", "structure": {"line_index": 25, "char_count": 6}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 5, 4, 4, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["gan1", "nei5", "si3", "gwo3", "cin1", "zau6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "試過", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "遷就", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0024", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0026", "paragraph_id": "para_06"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0026", "text": "痛也不分手先至悟透人世裏 有一些價值", "structure": {"line_index": 26, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 5, 3, 3, 9, 3, 4, 2, 4, 0, 4, 5, 5, 3, 3, 4, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["tung3", "jaa5", "bat1", "fan1", "sau2", "sin1", "zi3", "ng6", "tau3", "jan4", "sai3", "leoi5", "jau5", "jat1", "se1", "gaa3", "zik6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "痛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "分手", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "先至悟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "透", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "人世", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "裏", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一些", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "價值", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0025", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0027", "paragraph_id": "para_07"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0027", "text": "是比愛恨大 要補這個深溝 憑著愛不足夠", "structure": {"line_index": 27, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 9, 4, 2, 2, 4, 9, 5, 4, 3, 3, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["si6", "bei2", "oi3", "han6", "daai6", "jiu3", "bou2", "ze5", "go3", "sam1", "kau1", "pang4", "zoek6", "oi3", "bat1", "zuk1", "gau3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛恨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "大", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "補", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "深溝", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "憑著", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "愛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "足夠", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0026", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0028", "paragraph_id": "para_07"}}
{"id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0028", "text": "轉個時代 我想跟你 相廝守", "structure": {"line_index": 28, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 4, 0, 2, 5, 9, 3, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zyun2", "go3", "si4", "doi6", "ngo5", "soeng2", "gan1", "nei5", "si1", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "轉個", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "時代", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "廝守", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "俏郎君", "artists": ["張敬軒"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_6850", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0027", "next_line_id": "lyr_5byg5pWs6L2p_Njg1MA_0029", "paragraph_id": "para_08"}}
